question: Within a radius of 130 kilometers, which fast food restaurant can I find on the route towards Faith Arena, Surprise, AZ from Holiday Inn Hotel & Suites Phoenix Airport North, Phoenix, AZ?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-111.986458 33.464407)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-112.371855 33.62819)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-111.986458 33.464407)',4326)::geography, 130000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-111.986458 33.464407)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

[3].display_name: Holiday Inn Hotel & Suites Phoenix Airport North, Phoenix, AZ

poi.poi_name: Holiday Inn Hotel & Suites Phoenix Airport North
